@deftypefn {Function File} {} h2norm (@var{sys})
Computes the 
@iftex
@tex
$ { \cal H }_2 $
@end tex
@end iftex
@ifinfo
H-2
@end ifinfo
norm of a system data structure (continuous time only).

Reference:
Doyle, Glover, Khargonekar, Francis, @cite{State-Space Solutions to Standard} 
